[ READ-ME - Wed Sep 14 16:39:02 BST 1988 - ISODE idist utility notes - /jpo ]

     This directory contains the sources to idist - an rdist analogue
     for use with ISODE.

     The idist responder should be a dynamic responder as its first
     actions are to set the user-id which is ireversible for most users.

Julian.
